## Storage Layout

- Root folder = database name
- `db/` ŌĆö Database properties (manifest; defaultMaxShardSize 20MB; storageBackend: "text" | "binary")
- `Tables/` ŌĆö User tables; each folder has `<TableName>.txt` or `.bin` (per storageBackend), `_STOC.txt`/`.bin`, `_PK.txt`/`.idx`, `_FK_*.txt`/`.idx`, `_INX_*.txt`/`.idx`
- `~System/` ŌĆö System metadata (prefix `~` = engine-managed)
- `Views/`, `Procedures/`, `Functions/` ŌĆö Phase 6 (views, stored procedures, functions)

